        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto" color="#000000">
          <h2 style="font-size:20px;line-height:1.2;font-weight:500; margin-top:16px !important">Hostage execution</h2>
        </mj-text>
         <mj-image padding="10px 12px" width="600px" src="https://www.geopolitics.world/email/images/gp-dec-6-1.jpg" alt="Hostage execution" href="https://www.geopolitics.world" />
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
          <p style="font-size:16px;line-height:1.4;">The Israeli military recently <a href="https://edition.cnn.com/2024/12/04/middleeast/israel-hostages-airstrike-hamas-intl-latam/index.html" target="_Blank">announced</a> that a February 14 airstrike in <a href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/wtsS1LrUYGJSZwzZ6" target="_Blank">Khan Younis</a>, southern Gaza, may have led Hamas to execute six Israeli hostages, whose bodies were later found in August. An investigation revealed that the hostages likely survived the initial strike but were subsequently killed by militants, who themselves perished from the secondary effects of the attack. IDF spokesperson Daniel Hagari said they were not able to determine the cause of death due to the amount of time passed between the shooting and the forensic examination.</p>
          <p style="font-size:16px;line-height:1.4;">The broader conflict, now over 14 months long, has <a href="https://edition.cnn.com/2024/07/06/middleeast/palestinians-displaced-gaza-israel-intl/index.html" target="_Blank">displaced</a> most of Gaza’s population, many of whom face famine-like conditions, especially in the north. International aid deliveries have been severely <a href="https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2024/12/1/unrwa-pauses-aid-through-key-gaza-crossing-as-hunger-stalks-palestinians#:~:text=The%20UN%20agency%20for%20Palestinian%20refugees%20has%20halted,as%20widespread%20hunger%20and%20deadly%20Israeli%20bombardments%20continue." target="_Blank">restricted</a>, compounding the suffering of civilians. Amidst the chaos, the Israeli army has released an official <a href="https://www.aa.com.tr/en/middle-east/israeli-army-admits-targeting-humanitarian-area-in-gaza-s-khan-younis/3414654#:~:text=The%20Israeli%20army%20on%20Thursday%20admitted%20that%20it,airstrike%20killed%2023%20Palestinians%20and%20injured%20dozens%20more." target="_Blank">statement</a> that it has carried out a “precise air attack” against a Hamas operative, which saw the death of 23 Palestinians, including women and children. Calls for a <a href="https://apnews.com/article/israel-hamas-gaza-geasefire-negotiations-qatar-d09bb192b298adb3fa76d0e819721fdf" target="_Blank">ceasefire</a> have gained momentum from the truce in Lebanon with Hezbollah.​</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-divider border-width="1px" border-style="solid" border-color="lightgrey" padding="10px 12px" />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
